message: Define and throw a dedicated exception instead of using a generic one.
Use the primitive boolean expression here.
Rename this field "ERROR_THROWN" to match the regular expression '^[a-z][a-zA-Z0-9]*$'.
Remove the "filesToCompact" field and declare it as a local variable in the relevant methods.
Make the enclosing method "static" or remove this set.
Remove useless curly braces around statement (sonar.java.source not set. Assuming 8 or greater.)
